==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: chéng zhě wéi wáng, bài zhě wéi kòu
===Etymology===
Literally: He who wins becomes king while he who loses becomes a bandit.
===Proverb===
'''[[成]][[者]][[為]][[王]]，[[敗]][[者]][[為]][[寇]]'''
# The spoils go to the victor.
===Alternate forms===
[[成者为王，败者为寇]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
